import { ThemeProvider } from "@emotion/react"
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom"

import { AppRoutes } from "./routes"
import { LightTheme } from "./shared/themes"


function App() {


	return (
		<ThemeProvider theme={LightTheme}>
			<BrowserRouter>

				<AppRoutes />
					
			</BrowserRouter>
		</ThemeProvider>
	)
}

export default App
